### Start Gate first
### rimuru gate start --approvals --port 19710

GET http://127.0.0.1:19710/gate/overview

### Create a Soul
POST http://127.0.0.1:19710/sessions
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "sessionId": "demo"
}

### Send a message
POST http://127.0.0.1:19710/sessions/demo/message
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "prompt": "Explain this workspace in three bullets."
}

### Stream a message with Server-Sent Events
POST http://127.0.0.1:19710/sessions/demo/stream
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "prompt": "Stream a short status report."
}

### Call a Rune; write/execute/network risks may queue a Pact
POST http://127.0.0.1:19710/runes/call
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "workspace.search",
  "sessionId": "demo",
  "input": {
    "pattern": "Rimuru",
    "include": "*.md"
  }
}

### Review pending Pacts
GET http://127.0.0.1:19710/approvals

### Inspect audit events
GET http://127.0.0.1:19710/audit?limit=25
